<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2008-03-01</DATELINE><TITLE>Thiol-based angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 inhibitors: P1′ modifications for the exploration of the S1′ subsite</TITLE><BODY>Abstract Explorations of the S1′ subsite of ACE2 via modifications of the P1′ methylene biphenyl moiety of thiol-based metalloprotease inhibitors led to improvements in ACE2 selectivity versus ACE and NEP, while maintaining potent ACE2 inhibition.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>